<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="h-full">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sitio en Construcción</title>
  <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
</head>
<body class="h-full bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center px-6">

  <div class="max-w-md w-full text-center space-y-8 p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100">

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-amber-50 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-amber-800 ring-1 ring-inset ring-amber-600/20">
        Próximamente
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
        Sección en Construcción
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base text-slate-500">
        Estamos trabajando duro para traerte una gran experiencia. Esta función estará disponible muy pronto.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-2">
      <button onclick="window.history.back()" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-md shadow-blue-500/20 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 cursor-pointer">
        Volver atrás
      </button>
    </div>
    
  </div>

</body>
</html>